         I was looking this up earlier, according to some of the posts on Allakhazam, 12 turn ins (48 braids) takes you from Apprehensive to Indiff and another 12 takes you to Amiable.  Both of these faction catagories are 100 faction pts wide, so it looks like each turn in is roughly 8 faction pts or 2 pts/braid.</P><P>Suetekh<BR>Necromancer of 34 Reanimations<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
